eventText: John is asking for two developer contact names, email, phone numbers, in case there are some issues during the app upload on 13 Feb.
Shrinath, Piyush sends the minor_server_update.zip file to Shantanu.
Shantanu forwards the minor server update zip file to John.
John needs an updated APK, with stage path and latest “My Tools” fix, for testing this improvement ticket. John also asks to increase the version code.
Shantanu informs John that wrong apk file is uploaded and online. The online still has the myTools bug in it.
